{
  "stem": "27767.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we were growing up, we had-- we had the friends from my school, and the boys I grew up with.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one was like Mickey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The other one was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other one was Herschel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we grew up together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we got a little older, 13, 14, usually Saturday we went there to the mountains, because this town was a town in the middle of a mountain.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The mountains were around the town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was about two miles, three miles, four miles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It depends which place we went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We all went on a hike to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we played around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We played with the boys and girls Rummy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that was especially, Monopoly, and other place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very busy with studying, all of us, because we didn't have too much time, free time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially when I was already-- after the Hungarian came in, they didn't allow me to go to the high school, because it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't allow Jews to the high school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- my mother wanted very much we should go and graduate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we start-- we went to college [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- this was [INAUDIBLE] was a Jewish gymnasium, officially recognized Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we learned at home in private.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to do the exams there once a month, or every three weeks or so, because we couldn't afford to go there, and sleep over there, and get a room, and bed, and food, whatever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It also about 200 miles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he traveled-- he had to hire a wagon with a horse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he didn't go every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went twice a week or so, maybe three times a week, maybe once a week, depends.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
